description:
This is a bonus product.
Note: Available until February 28th, 2022.

■Contents
Lu Lingqi is added under the following clothing and armor types in Female Custom Parts.
Bottom Type / Helmet Type / Chest Type / Arm Type / Leg Type

■To Use
In Edit Mode, select Female from Gender, and then select the content from Bottom Types or the corresponding type of armor.

Note: Please note that some of these might be made available for separate purchase at a later time.
name: Female Custom Lu Lingqi Set
